  "title": "1 year contract Patient Service Associate (Outram / Tampines) - $2500 Fixed #HKH",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Greet and register patients</li><li>Schedule patient appointment</li><li>Coordinate specialists' consultation referrals</li><li>Handle payments and respond to patient enquiries in a courteous and professional manner</li><li>Manage patient concerns, ensuring timely resolution and escalation when necessary</li><li>Communicate effectively with patients to provide a high level of customer service</li><li>Will be stationed at Health monitoring station based on roster. Involved in taking height / weight and blood pressure for patients at Health monitoring station</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum GCE ‘N’ level</li><li>No exp needed, training provided</li><li>Healthcare experience will be an advantage but not compulsory</li></ul><p><strong>$2500 (Fixed salary)</strong></p><p><strong>Tampines / Outram Clinic </strong></p><p><br /></p><p>Interested candidates, please forward your resume to <strong>kevynhuang@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>Consultant: Huang Jingsheng Kevyn (R1333338)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (99C4599)</p>",
